Michael Buckley died after being hit by a shopping trolley at Marks & Spencer . 
  Melanie Buck is accused of killing the 60-year-old widower in a 'trolley rage incident' She allegedly became frustrated because the store was 'gridlocked' with shoppers . 
  Mr Buckley fell to the floor and broke his wrist and thigh bones in the incident . 
  He died three months after the incident on December 22, 2012 . 
  Buck has pleaded not guilty to manslaughter and GBH at Croydon Crown Court . 
 